   Introduction

   FirstGov for Employers is a joint effort among the Department of Labor,
   Internal Revenue Service, Small Business Administration, Social
   Security Administration, Treasury, States, and Simplified Tax and Wage
   Reporting System. The site provides resources and cross-agency
   information for employers, as well as new and established businesses.

   Important News About the Web Site
   The FirstGov for Employers site is moving and being enhanced. Check
   back for updates on the status of this new enhanced site for employers
   and businesses.

   U.S. Government Responds to September 11 Tragedy
   The Office of FirstGov staff has compiled a list of government and
   other resources for victims, families, and friends of the vicious
   terrorist attack on New York, Pennsylvania, and Washington, D.C.




